{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan an Nasai","section":{"21":"The Book of Funerals"},"section_detail":{"21":{"hadithnumber_first":1818,"hadithnumber_last":2089,"arabicnumber_first":1818,"arabicnumber_last":2089}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1945,"arabicnumber":1945,"text":"Rapporté par Salim : Son père lui a raconté qu’il était avec le Prophète ﷺ, Abu Bakr, 'Umar et 'Uthman رضي الله عنهم, marchant devant un cortège funèbre","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":21,"hadith":128}}]}